_header: Saint Kenelm in England was I-come of good strain
Subjects: saints’ lives; Kenelm, saint, life of
_description: A variant of the Life of St. Kenelm in the South English Legendary

BodEngPoeta1.First Lines:
SEint Kenelm in Engelonde was i come of goode streoneA good kynges
                    sone he was and his Modur was Qweene…
BodEngPoeta1.Last Lines:
…At Winchecumbe is þat bodi i don in one schrineIhesu for
                    þe loue of him vs schilde from helle pyne Amen

Lam223.First Lines:
SAynt kenelme of Englond was comen of godestreneA kynges sone he
                    was & his moder a quene…
Lam223.Last Lines:
…At Wynchcombe is þat body done in a shryneNow Ihesu for
                    þe love of hym vs shilde fro helle pyne Amen
